{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"beda109b99","title":"空军要全力以赴务开入侵之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ca7e4869ea","index":0,"year":1957,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"beda109b99"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"1021e61abf","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长，主持军委日常工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"eeefe47a7c","type":"title","text":"空军要全力以赴务歼人侵之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"},{"id":"1021e61abf","type":"paragraph","text":"退彭德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"},{"id":"b2543e6625","type":"paragraph","text":"非常必要。请你督促空军全力以赴，务外入侵之敌。请考虑我空军一九五八年进入福建的问题","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"},{"id":"1640443977","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"},{"id":"8332f2201e","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"},{"id":"95e927b708","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东在中国人民解放军副总参谋长陈度1957年12月9日关子台湾飞机侵入大陆活动情况和加强内地防空作战部署给彭德怀并中共中央军委的报告上写的批语。报告说，台湾飞机今年多次偷入大陆沿海重要城市和内地，空投了大批反动传单和“慰问品”，在群众中造成极坏影响。由于部队有些领导同志对防空作战思想上不重视和领导上检查督促不严，对肇入内地蒋机均未能将其击落。为了迅速扭转这种状况，我们已布置空军和各军区今后必须采取一切积极有效的措施，对可能入侵内地的蒋机给以应有打击，并力求将其击落。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99"}],"page":{"id":"544b95dd47","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"beda109b99","start":382,"end":382}}}},"__N_SSG":true}